my online game is all bout keepin it classy, keepin it real, and keepin it professional. no time for playin around with sarcasm, emojis, or all that jazz. gotta get my point across, ya know what Im sayin? Im here to educate, advocate, and make a difference. so like, Stanford, its time to get your act together, focus on sustainability, and ditch that overdevelopment vibe. lets keep it green, keep it real, and keep it #SustainableStanford! 🌿🌍
